metadata.name: The JP Effect
metadata.description: Welcome to JP's Metaverse presented by King Saladeen, where JP the MoneyBear has dedicated himself to encouraging others to overcome their doubts and find success. Here, the difference-makers and dream chasers have found a place to call home and they are dedicated to supporting each other in achieving their ambitions.
